<title>Án Aıtamyn Men</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bul qoıylym emes
 Iem, shyn júrekti
 Ǵıbadat dep tileımin
 Sezimge batýǵa
 Men múldem umtylmaımyn
 Men tek sen úshin aıtamyn

[C1]
   Oo Án aıtamyn men
   Shyn júrekpen aıtsam tek
   Tek saǵan meniń Iem
   Bilmeımin nege
   Jasadym jasandy ony
   Ol Seniń dańqyń úshin
   (Ooo Ooo)

[V2]
 Kemeldiktiń ornyna
 Júregimdi qaladyń
 Bar nársemdi beremin
 Bir sátke sozylatyn ánnen de
 Adaldyqqa toly ómir súremin
 Ánim tek maqsatpen shyrqala bersin -
 Aqyr sońynda, Bar dańqqa laıyqsyń</lyrics>
</song>